      "content": "Look, I'm not asking you to help me break any laws, I'm talking about a specific intelligence threat. Standard bank security is exactly what these remnant groups exploit because they have legacy access to the routing systems. If you don't understand the distinction between a standard fraud attempt and an old-regime surveillance operation, then you aren't being very useful here. They don't follow \"regulations,\" they bypass them.",
